Package at.tuwien.ifs.somtoolbox.output.labeling

Provides implementations of labeling algorithms to assign semantic labels to SOM units.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Labeler
    Defines basic functionality for Labelers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLabeler
    This class provides basic functionality all Labelers can use.
    LabelSOM
    Implements the LabelSOM labelling method, as described in A.
    LagusKeywordLabeler
    Implements the Keyword selection labelling method, as described in Lagus, K.
    UnitWords
    This class is used for saving the word frequencies of word cocurrences.
    UnitWordsMap
    Contains all UnitWords for the map and can be used to calculate goodnesses of words and select the best words from an unit.
